metadata.name: Universe
metadata.description:
I want to present you the first work in the limited collection "Color Madness". This NFT is dedicated to the theme of space and my perception of the world at a given moment in time. For many years, space has attracted millions of people. It can give an answer to any question and at the same time is so silent.

This is 1 of 6 Limited NFT.

The model has given permission to use the material.

The model's Instagram: https://instagram.com/krissgaidukova
